la`\n  - Replaced the placeholder test with a dedicated `ReflectionUtilsTest`.\n  - Added an interface-based Mockito Scala test using `thenAnswer(PartialFunction)` to drive `InvocationOnMockOps.argsAsTuple` and `ReflectionUtils.listToTuple`.\n  - Added a `ReflectionUtils.setFinalStatic` test against a Scala module `MODULE$` field to exercise the Java 17+ Unsafe-based path.\n\n- `tests/src/org.mockito/mockito-scala_2.13/2.0.0/src/test/resources/mockito-extensions/org.mockito.plugins.MockMaker`\n  - Added the required proxy mock maker resource with exactly:\n    `org.mockito.internal.creation.proxy.ProxyMockMaker`\n\nAlso removed the scaffold-only placeholder file:\n\n- `tests/src/org.mockito/mockito-scala_2.13/2.0.0/src/test/scala/org_mockito/mockito_scala_2_13/Mockito_scala_2_13Test.scala`\n\nI did not run tests, per the workflow instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0757c4a88c6caded016a28d4f7c7848197bfdb2270f5494258\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 282, "output": 1494, "cacheRead": 28160, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29936, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781060824892, "responseId": "resp_0757c4a88c6caded016a28d4d9b48881978f10993f0782a98c"}}
[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering static field issues**\n\nI’m facing a potential issue with modifying a field marked final static in a native image, maybe related to `UnsupportedFeature`. Unsafe static field operations might still work, but I’d need to test that. Okay, so `setFinalStatic` is used for `withObjectMocked`, and it's supported behavior with the library. I need to think about covering all 17Minus call sites. However, it seems that under Java 21, this could remain unreachable without forcing an unsupported path.\n\n**Evaluating static path compatibility**\n\nThe `setFinalStatic17Minus` path is meant for older Java versions and isn’t supported on JDK21, so it shouldn't be used. I could set the `java.version` system property with `@BeforeAll` before using any ReflectionUtils, but that could lead all `setFinalStatic` invocations to rely on the 17Minus path on JDK21, which would likely fail. That’s not a good approach. I need to rethink how to handle this situation properly!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0757c4a88c6caded016a28d4da6a4c81978187f5438e6274ff\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKNT3AQAhGiIhQPR004Ga_QBkxutHNVcYZOlzYO_HwWn12E7DaNkv4tgE8NWDDhWqaQxGI_rJdlLzqjtImqGPMYvUKGMeMoipvAb-2yheJ4xjXP35Pa6tVBRSifPOC9jZDMqN1fJbxUtG5WdyJsUTBbWs7fbwIUNsUe8ZMwY5nXo2keqNpunjDHSUFcrGS_KP4W_vfRsJHQ7u_XG65dJ0P9tERInvhHBv0mbgbI37vp87E0cKTQKjfINyv9386ZS0Zwr-vKJqlrd-Cq_WaFg30aCcqF7s-gLDnpqgFSqrqQ7POWgL13ZuQl3sl_coUyQQM28X5RG1jPHFz5U2bHC9V42LqAbwAl9kpTBcBg2k2JlyIRyemWejw4khRsj6UEdwJNPMuMic71e1RdBdI-C3ZrmEoTelcC36d3-wt6k37C95kwaFuAiuufMEpVr-CKYJ1rU897WqdXxQnw4bVfytpUAgb5DEVF1FggpQiq6KBoIUxnXLmuVWMX2jnZYr4xZGCTQFkYfWpBkqyWHNM3wt24mFiMScgqXIOxZXij6ClvZbd8pgcUiZ_soUD-yAlP5QV03sFGzJg2lysuHjYvrUMMf7Zh9rb10_nvEj6K6hZQyF1pz4ET_hBRJimtspT3n7kEVZrzFLX_qX7l06Zi3GNIWlDCyZom4kj26NJpsHluXocqdm-t46Xa2x_7P3H-FWuPLrkwi7f9PenvoXzWPuCpRuvKvrMjaSY7ALZ-52BN8W0Npqy6pd