alStatic17Minus`, which is guarded by:\n\n```scala\nif (JavaVersion < 17)\n  setFinalStatic17Minus(field, newValue)\nelse\n  setFinalStatic17Plus(field, newValue)\n```\n\nOn the project’s JDK 21 test/runtime setup, normal public API behavior always routes to `setFinalStatic17Plus`, which is already covered by the current `ReflectionUtilsTest`.\n\nReaching the remaining sites would require an unsupported test technique, such as:\n\n- changing `java.version` before `ReflectionUtils` initializes and forcing a legacy Java path on JDK 21,\n- mutating the private `JavaVersion` value,\n- reflectively invoking private `setFinalStatic17Minus`,\n- or loading Mockito Scala through a separate custom classloader.\n\nThose approaches would violate the task rules requiring supported behavior through normal public API and avoiding direct reflection/internal manipulation. Therefore, the remaining call sites should stay uncovered for this JDK/native-image target.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0757c4a88c6caded016a28d77c469081979c5e21eba4eb917d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 5703, "output": 1704, "cacheRead": 26112, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33519, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781061450447, "responseId": "resp_0757c4a88c6caded016a28d74c9e648197adccf7a52301997c"}}
